<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />早安！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，午安！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，你好！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好呀，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搬家的行李終於整理到一個段落了，<delay frames="40" />
這下我總算能放心開始新生活了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我搬來的第一天，你沒來看我，<delay20 />
我現在說不定會感到更不安呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總算是把家裡整理完了，<delay20 />
剛才正在和島上的人們打招呼呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我很感謝你喔。<delay frames="40" />
你能在我搬來的第一天來看看我，<delay20 />
真的讓我很高興。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經漸漸習慣這裡的生活囉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哪些地方有什麼東西也大多記住了，<delay20 />
就算不看地圖也不要緊呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡的生活比我想像的更便利，<delay20 />
島上的人也都對我很好，幫了我很大的忙呢。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這一個星期<delay8 />我打算在島上到處逛逛，<delay20 />
多多熟悉這裡的生活呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然現在還有很多我不了解的事，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但周遭的事物看起來全都很新奇，<delay8 />
感覺很有趣呢。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天會跟你搭話，<delay20 />
是因為想跟你打聲招呼，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順便送你一點小禮物當見面禮。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天有東西想送給你唷。<delay frames="40" />
這就叫<delay8 />見面禮吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就別客氣，儘管收下吧！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
在我之前住的島上非常受歡迎呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道合不合你的喜好，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但不嫌棄的話，希望你能使用看看喔。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
是我從故鄉帶來的。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是<delay8 />評價很不錯的伴手禮唷。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不嫌棄的話，就請拿去用吧。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然叫住你真是抱歉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我大概會這座島上住好一段時間，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後還請多多關照了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那麼請讓我再好好說一次，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望今後也能和你好好相處唷。<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今後可能會給你添麻煩也說不定，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你有什麼事想跟我說，<delay20 />
就儘管說別客氣唷，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>